<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 15:16:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，中国电池巨头宁德时代聘请银行进行上半年香港上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-battery-giant-catl-hires-banks-first-half-hong-kong-float-sources-say-2025-01-13/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国电池巨头宁德时代已聘请摩根大通和美国银行等银行参与香港上市事宜，这可能是该市 2025 年最大规模的上市之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:52:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-battery-giant-catl-hires-banks-first-half-hong-kong-float-sources-say-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>出租人SMBC Aviation首席执行官表示几乎所有飞机都被延误</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/ceo-lessor-smbc-aviation-says-almost-every-aircraft-being-delayed-2025-01-13/</link><description>飞机租赁巨头SMBC Aviation Capital的负责人周一表示，波音和空客交付的几乎每架飞机都被推迟，随后又补充说，发动机制造商在解决问题方面已做出了轻微改进。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/ceo-lessor-smbc-aviation-says-almost-every-aircraft-being-delayed-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>西藏上周地震后发生两次强烈余震</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/earthquakes-hit-tibets-tingri-county-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国西藏地区的一个农村县仍感受到上周 6.8 级地震的震感，周一晚上又发生了两次相隔不到一分钟的强烈余震。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:22:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/earthquakes-hit-tibets-tingri-county-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>OpenAI 敦促美国优先考虑人工智能资金和监管，以保持领先于中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/openai-urges-us-prioritize-ai-funding-regulation-stay-ahead-china-2025-01-13/</link><description>OpenAI 周一阐述了美国人工智能发展的愿景，称美国需要外部投资和支持性监管，才能在新兴技术的竞争中保持领先于中国。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/openai-urges-us-prioritize-ai-funding-regulation-stay-ahead-china-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国誓言扩大单边免签国家名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-expand-list-unilateral-visa-free-countries-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国政府周一发布的措施显示，中国将扩大单边免签国家名单并延长免签停留期限。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-expand-list-unilateral-visa-free-countries-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大旗下子公司收到香港法院的清算令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-unit-receives-liquidation-order-hong-kong-court-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国恒大周一表示，香港一家法院已下令将其一个主要离岸子公司清盘，这是这家陷入困境的开发商清算人取得的一系列法律胜利中的最新一起。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-unit-receives-liquidation-order-hong-kong-court-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：因债券困扰，标普 500 指数抹去了大选后的涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-13/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:17:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>德国高端汽车制造商在中国和德国的销售因经济放缓而遭受重创</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-group-annual-sales-fall-weak-demand-china-germany-2025-01-13/</link><description>销量数据显示，2024 年德国高端汽车制造商在国内和中国都遭受重创，因为经济不确定且电动汽车销售低于预期，较富裕的消费者抑制了购买。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:10:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-group-annual-sales-fall-weak-demand-china-germany-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国新的人工智能芯片规则将如何运作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/how-new-ai-chip-rule-us-will-work-2025-01-13/</link><description>该规则规范了最复杂的人工智能应用所需的美国人工智能芯片和技术的流动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/how-new-ai-chip-rule-us-will-work-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国收紧对全球人工智能芯片流动的控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-tightens-its-grip-ai-chip-flows-across-globe-2025-01-13/</link><description>美国政府表示，将进一步限制人工智能芯片和技术出口，瓜分全球，将先进计算能力保留在美国及其盟友手中，同时寻找更多方式阻止中国进入。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-tightens-its-grip-ai-chip-flows-across-globe-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达表示新规定将削弱美国在人工智能领域的领导地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/nvidia-says-new-rule-will-weaken-us-leadership-ai-2025-01-13/</link><description>英伟达批评拜登政府为加强华盛顿对全球人工智能芯片流动的控制而采取的新举措，称该规定将危及美国目前在人工智能领域的领导地位。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/nvidia-says-new-rule-will-weaken-us-leadership-ai-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>英国和毛里求斯表示查戈斯群岛谈判取得良好进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-mauritius-say-good-progress-made-chagos-islands-talks-2025-01-13/</link><description>英国和毛里求斯周一表示，谈判在敲定查戈斯群岛主权协议（包括美英军事基地）方面取得了良好进展，伦敦希望在唐纳德·特朗普就职前签署该协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 09:57:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-mauritius-say-good-progress-made-chagos-islands-talks-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国制裁收紧对俄罗斯石油的控制，中国和印度寻求新的供应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-india-refiners-scour-world-oil-supplies-us-sanctions-curb-russian-supply-2025-01-13/</link><description>许多贸易商周一表示，由于美国对俄罗斯生产商和油轮的新制裁将成为迄今为止限制向莫斯科最大客户发货的最有效措施，中国和印度炼油商正在寻求替代原油供应。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 09:50:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-india-refiners-scour-world-oil-supplies-us-sanctions-curb-russian-supply-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>协会数据显示2025年中国汽车出口增速将放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-vehicle-export-growth-slow-2025-association-data-shows-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国汽车工业协会 (CAAM) 周一公布的数据显示，今年中国汽车出口量预计将增长 5.8%，达到 620 万辆，较 2024 年 19.3% 的增幅有所降温。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:58:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-vehicle-export-growth-slow-2025-association-data-shows-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>陆军参谋长表示，印度不会在冬季减少中国边境驻军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-looking-reduce-troops-along-northern-frontier-winter-army-chief-says-2025-01-13/</link><description>印度陆军参谋长周一表示，印度不打算在冬季减少北部边境的军队数量，并补充说，印度将根据与中国的谈判结果审查夏季部署。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-looking-reduce-troops-along-northern-frontier-winter-army-chief-says-2025-01-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>